# 03 - Loops

## 📖 About

This folder contains Python programs and practice notebooks related to loops.

Loops are used to execute a block of code repeatedly, making programs shorter, cleaner, and more efficient.

---

## 📚 Topics Covered

- Introduction to Loops
- For Loop
- While Loop
- Nested Loops
- Break Statement
- Continue Statement
- Pass Statement
- Pattern Programs
- Mini Projects

---

## 🎯 Learning Objectives

After completing this folder, you will be able to:

- Understand why loops are used.
- Write programs using `for` and `while` loops.
- Control loop execution using `break`, `continue`, and `pass`.
- Solve pattern-based programming questions.
- Build beginner-friendly mini projects using loops.

